cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a new method for estimating mutual information using neural networks. It also involves the estimation of entropy, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) sub-category. The paper's focus on neural networks and their application to mutual information estimation suggests that it could also be classified under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper's use of mutual information in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE) further supports these potential sub-categories.
